   Sort Method: quicksort  Memory: xxxkB
   ->  Custom Scan (DocumentDBApiExplainQueryScan) (actual rows=6 loops=1)
         namespaceName: ord_coll_ordered_db.ord_comp_pos_neg
         indexName: idx_comp_ab_en_strength3
         indexKey: {"a": 1,"b": 1}
         isMultiKey: false
         startBounds: ["a": ["cherry", "cherry"], "b": [MinKey, "red"]]
